long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The NAEP assessment extension to set up and monitor assessment delivery administration on the ChromeOS-managed devices. The primary purpose of the extension is to be able to monitor the network and device health during the assessment via Chrome APIs.
